                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-637" type="given" value="SAMUEL STEPHEN"></interp>SAMUEL STEPHEN DUCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at No. 8, Union-court—my yard adjoins the yard of this house—I found this piece of lead down our back area.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420404-name-638" type="witnessName">
