                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This it the sort of pipe which was fixed to the ceiling.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420404-name-639" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-639" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-639" type="surname" value="CULL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-639" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM CULL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a plumber—I put the leaden pipe upon the house, thirteen years ago, and know my own joints in it—the house belongs to Sarah Pennington and others.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went to the public-house bat the privy was engaged, and knowing the people in this court I went there; and when in the cellar this lady came down—I told her I had been to the water-closet—she would not let me go—I went into the yard to go to the water-closet and they laid hold of me.</p>
